signify a dataset that records the health state and failure occurrence of a system at unit time during the system lifecycle. || Duplicate features can be found by correlation analysis with other features and need to be excluded from a dataset. || Dataset partition divides the entire dataset into training and testing datasets. || A training dataset can be further segregated into training and validation dataset s, if necessary. || The training dataset is used to learn the data for generating the models, whereas the validation dataset is used to measure the learning error to check the correctness of the learning models. || The testing dataset is used to measure the prediction error to verify the prediction accuracy when the models are applied to a target system."
